    RedeemFertiliserAction, RedeemSwordAction, RedeemTicketAction
    public abstract class RedeemAction
extends edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Action
    Provides methods for its subclasses to redeem items. Abstract class created to ensure that its subclasses implement its superclass' abstract methods.
